Package project2

Class ClassSchedule

java.lang.Object
project2.ClassSchedule
public class ClassSchedule extends Object
ClassSchedule is the class to contain list of fitness classes. It's essentials are similar to MemberDatabase class.
Author:
Ryan S. Lee, Elliott Ng
